data.description: Presenting an exceptional opportunity to build your dream home in the heart of Lehigh Acres, FL. This vacant lot at 2805 58th St offers a prime location and ample space to bring your vision to life. Situated in a vibrant community, this blank canvas invites you to create a custom residence tailored to your unique preferences. With nearby amenities and a serene neighborhood setting, this lot embodies the potential for a truly special home.
